Anthony Cistaro https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anthony_Cistaro 0 Anthony Cistaro (born June 8, 1963 in Kirksville, Missouri), is an American actor. At an early age he moved to San Francisco, California, where his father worked as a teacher and counselor, while his mother worked in the home, caring for the family. In later years she worked as a program assistant in academic departments. Cistaro attended St. Ignatius College Prep., graduating in 1981.
